data.description: ***ELIGIBLE FOR USDA 100% FINANCING***     MOTIVATED SELLERS.      $1,500.00 TOWARDS closing on any contract with a closing date on or before January 19, 2024    Welcome to Your Dream Home in Cartersville, GA! Explore the perfect blend of style and functionality in this 3-bedroom, 2-bath gem situated within the highly sought-after community of The Stiles. As of 10/23, revel in the comfort of a brand-new AC unit, ensuring a cool and inviting atmosphere year-round.      Step inside and immerse yourself in the open floor plan on the main level, seamlessly connecting the living, dining, and kitchen areas across the entire width of the home. The heart of this residence is the impeccably designed kitchen, where efficiency meets elegance. Revel in the upgrades, including a fireplace, LVP flooring, a kitchen island, and wrought iron stair railings, enhancing the overall aesthetic.              With ample countertop workspace, a center island, a sink that overlooks the backyard, and a pantry for storage, every culinary need is met with ease. Venture upstairs to discover your private retreats – the owner's ensuite boasts a spacious closet for all your wardrobe essentials, along with two additional bedrooms and a well-appointed bath. Convenience is paramount with the strategically placed laundry room, making chores a breeze.      Upstairs, a versatile loft area offers space for relaxation or entertainment, ensuring every inch of this home is utilized to its fullest potential. This is more than a home; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to call this Cartersville residence in The Stiles your own!    NO WAITLIST... MOVE IN NOW!
